<SECOND>AM-Paraguay-Election, 5th Ld-Writethru, a0923,0667</SECOND>
<HEAD>Stroessner Wins Eighth Term With 89 Percent Of Vote</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 7 grafs to RESTORE reference to length of
