 Method: Primary Date: Tuesday, February 16 Presidential filing deadline: Friday, December 18, 1987 Candidates filed: <PERSON> Bruce </PERSON> <PERSON> Babbitt </PERSON>, <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Dukakis </PERSON>, <PERSON> Richard </PERSON> <PERSON> Gephardt </PERSON>, <PERSON> Albert </PERSON> <PERSON> Gore </PERSON>, <PERSON> Gary </PERSON> <PERSON> Hart </PERSON>, <PERSON> Jesse </PERSON> <PERSON> Jackson </PERSON>, <PERSON> Paul </PERSON> <PERSON> Simon </PERSON> Pledged delegates: 18 Super delegates: 4 TOTAL: 22 Delegates allocated: Tuesday, February 16 Selection of delegates: Saturday, January 23 and Sunday, April 24 All of <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Hampshire </LOCATION>'s 18 pledged delegates to the Democratic National Convention will be allocated among presidential candidates in proportion to the results of the primary on Feb. 16.
