 <PERSON> Denis </PERSON> <PERSON> D. </PERSON> <PERSON> Gray </PERSON>, bureau chief for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Thailand </LOCATION>, covered <LOCATION> Cambodia </LOCATION> during the <LOCATION> Indochina </LOCATION> War and visits the country from his base in <LOCATION> Bangkok </LOCATION>.
